@startuml act_registration
!theme plain
title Activity Diagram: Registration & Authentication Flow

|User|
start
:Enter Registration Data\n(Username, Email, Password);

|System (Auth Service)|
:Validate Input;
:Generate 6-digit OTP;
:Send OTP via Email;

|User|
:Input OTP;

|System (Auth Service)|
if (Is OTP Valid & Not Expired?) then (Yes)
  :Create Account\n(Status: PENDING_ADMIN);
  :Emit "new_user_registered" Event;
else (No)
  :Return Error\n"Invalid/Expired OTP";
  stop
endif

|Admin|
:Receive Real-time Notification;
:Review New Account Details;
if (Approve Account?) then (Yes)
  |System (Auth Service)|
  :Update Status to ACTIVE;
  :Allow Login;
else (No)
  |System (Auth Service)|
  :Update Status to REJECTED\n(or Delete);
endif
stop
@enduml